      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved by its previous owner. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine condition, still carrying that new-car feel. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory, with every feature functioning perfectly and a complete service history to back it up. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly exceptional example that requires absolutely no investment or repairs.",
