    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The exterior has significant paint damage, rust spots, and several dents. The interior is heavily worn with tears in the upholstery and stained carpeting. Mechanically, the car requires several repairs to be fully reliable, and it currently has multiple warning lights illuminated on the dashboard.",
